---
title: Cheesy BBQ Beef Quesadillas & Avocado Salsa with Charred Corn & Sour Cream
description: These easy beef quesadillas are finished off in the oven — perfect for busy nights at home. Add the bold smokey BBQ flavours you
know and love, plus a bright and zingy avocado and pickled onion salsa and rich sour cream and these will quickly be your new favourites.
